<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>There is no longer a level cap on starting this quest. You can start at any level. This was changed after a string of complaints from Paladins who were new to the game and had already passed the required level before they found out about it. Many of those opted to restart their character, but it was deemed unfair and the cap was abolished.</font></td></tr></table>
