<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Duellist</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-11-17 20:04:37</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Our guild just killed Lucan a few days ago. Its not as hard as you might believe. Just need the right combo. Our bro, a lvl 46 pally asked for help and we responded. All it took was a 46 pally, 2 40 warriors, a 37 druid, and.. o yeah.. a 51 mage, heheh. The pet was enough to sway the tide in our favor, despite a higher lvl guard (forget who.. maybe Inofus) rearing his ugly head and beating on the other lvl 40 warrior, who had to zone. This was also immediately following myself and the other 40 warrior beating down Jentry (with some wicked sick heal luvin from our resident druid goddess).<BR>
<BR>
A tip: we used the sewer strategy in combination with the pull and hail trick. We used a passerby to hail Lucan at the EFP zone til the others returned to their post. Then we pulled Lucan back to the sewers by the NFP zone.<BR>
<BR>
In case it wasnt mentioned... u have to kill Lucan twice.. his undead self spawns from his corpse.. but is much much easier.<BR>
<BR>
And NO.. Lucan does NOT have LOH...<BR>
<BR>
Grats to our bro... ever closer to the FA... and a HUGE thx to the resident guild god for makin it possible (u know who u are)<BR>
<BR>
Duellist O'Nael<BR>
40th Warrior<BR>
KoL<BR>
Saryrn</font></td></tr></table>
